# Skin Cancer Detection — Project Rules

## Project Context
- Task: Binary skin lesion **segmentation** (ISIC 2018 Task 1)
- Dataset: ISIC2018_Task1_Input (images) + ISIC2018_Task1_GroundTruth (binary masks)
- Current best: **Dice=0.9021, IoU=0.8368** (U-Net + ResNet34 encoder + SCSE decoder, epoch 41)
- Goals: (1) Beat Dice > 0.90 với kiến trúc mới, (2) Deploy web app (FastAPI backend)

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11 (Conda env)
- PyTorch 2.x + AMP (`torch.amp`)
- Segmentation: `segmentation-models-pytorch >= 0.3` (SMP)
- Augmentation: `albumentations >= 1.3`
- Experiment tracking: W&B + local CSV/JSON fallback
- Config system: YAML với `_base_` inheritance + CLI dot-notation overrides
- Package: `src/` (editable install qua `pip install -e .`)

